    "Notably, the U 10 = 2.25 m s -1 case is outside the wind speed training range.",
    "The signal-to-noise ratio of PIV velocity measurements naturally degrades in near-surface areas due to various factors, including the reflection of high-intensity laser light off the surface and the presence of other background noise sources.",
